Installation Instructions
*************************

You will need the C++ owl libraries to build this project.
Get them from:
https://github.com/OwlPlatform/cpp-owl-common
and
https://github.com/OwlPlatform/cpp-owl-solver

Afterwards you can install this solver with cmake:
cmake .
make
make install

To configure variables used by cmake, such as your lib directory,
run `cmake --help` to find the appropriate command line parameters.
